# Supabase (login / signup étudiants)
# Google OAuth: Supabase Dashboard → Authentication → Providers → Google
#
# URL Configuration (CRITICAL — otherwise Google redirects to localhost):
#   Site URL:        https://belkou.online
#   Redirect URLs:   https://belkou.online/auth/callback
#                    http://localhost:8080/auth/callback
#
# Email confirmation — sender "BelKou" (not "Supabase Auth"):
#   Supabase Dashboard → Authentication → Emails → SMTP Settings
#   → Enable Custom SMTP, then:
#     Sender name:  BelKou
#     Sender email: profzoula@gmail.com
#     Host:         smtp.gmail.com
#     Port:         465  (si 587 échoue, essayez 465 avec SSL)
#     Username:     profzoula@gmail.com
#     Password:     Google App Password (https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords)
#   Si aucun email n'arrive: Supabase → Logs → Auth (erreurs SMTP)
#   Rate limit initial: ~30 emails/heure sur nouveau SMTP
#   Then Authentication → Emails → Templates → Confirm signup:
#     Subject: Confirmez votre compte BelKou
#
# Railway: add VITE_SITE_URL=https://belkou.online (needed at build time)
